     "12e4fc3e-3ee7-4fa7-97f0-1fd2acadf389"], Cell["\<\
the target relative accuracy, which sets Nsum via the nu_max law\
\>", "TableText",ExpressionUUID->"fe836459-e5b4-4cca-b991-b7db2defbca2"]},
   {Cell["", "ModInfo",ExpressionUUID->
